ch: 'Geen nazi-propaganda in museum'|website=Omroep Brabant|language=NL|access-date=2020-04-22}}</ref>\n\nThe movement also organizes an alternative remembrance of the [[February strike|February Strike]]. In contrast to the official remembrance, the remembrance of the CJB specifically celebrates the communist ideology of the strikers<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.voorwaarts.net/viering-februaristaking-2020-antifascisme-geef-je-door/|title=Viering Februaristaking 2020: Antifascisme Geef Je Door!|last=Feb 13|first=|last2=CJB|first2=|date=2020-02-13|website=Voorwaarts.net|language=nl-NL|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-22|last3=|last4=|last5=|last6=|last7=}}</ref>.<br />\n\n== International ==\nThe CJB participates in the Meeting of European Communist Youth Organizations (MECYO) and is a pending member of the [[World Federation of Democratic Youth]] (WFDY). It enjoys good bilateral relations with the [[Socialist German Workers Youth|SDAJ]] and the [[Comac (youth movement)|COMAC]]. The movement regularly organizes actions in solidarity with [[Cuba]], [[Venezuela]] and [[Bolivia]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.voorwaarts.net/succesvolle-politieke-bijeenkomst-imperialisme-of-socialisme-70-jaar-navo-100-jaar-komintern/|title=Succesvolle politieke bijeenkomst: \u2018Imperialisme of Socialisme? 70 jaar NAVO - 100 jaar Komintern'|last=Dec 17|first=|last2=|first2=|date=2019-12-17|website=Voorwaarts.net|language=nl|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-22|last3=|last4=|first4=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.voorwaarts.net/verklaring-ncpn-en-cjb-over-de-staatsgreep-in-bolivia/|title=Verklaring NCPN en CJB over de staatsgreep in Bolivia|last=Nov 15|first=|last2=|first2=|date=2019-11-15|website=Voorwaarts.net|language=nl-NL|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-22|last3=|last4=|last5=|last6=|first6=|last7=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.voorwaarts.net/verklaring-over-de-couppoging-in-